WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:11.333 --> 00:00:14.667
{\an8}Agatha Harkness.
You have betrayed your coven.

2
00:00:14.750 --> 00:00:15.917
Mother!

3
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.250
[chanting in Latin]

4
00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:19.792
[in English] No!

5
00:00:19.875 --> 00:00:22.125
[screams and gasps]

6
00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:27.875
[witches scream]

7
00:00:33.333 --> 00:00:35.042
[Rio] <i>I'll tell them where to find you.</i>

8
00:00:35.125 --> 00:00:38.125
Who. specifically?

9
00:00:38.208 --> 00:00:39.208
[Rio] <i>The Salem Seven.</i>

10
00:00:41.625 --> 00:00:42.667
Who is this child?

11
00:00:42.750 --> 00:00:45.000
-This is my pet. Say hi. Pet.
-Hi.

12
00:00:45.083 --> 00:00:46.417
Watch your back with Agatha.

13
00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:48.125
I know how people feel about her.

14
00:00:48.208 --> 00:00:50.833
[Jen] <i>She probably wouldn't recognize
her son if he was at her door.</i>

15
00:00:50.958 --> 00:00:53.292
{\an8}<i>They say no one knows
what happened to him.</i>

16
00:00:53.375 --> 00:00:56.583
[Agatha] <i>What if we summon
a backup Green Witch?</i>

17
00:00:58.083 --> 00:00:59.375
-[all gasp and scream]
-Surprise.

18
00:00:59.458 --> 00:01:00.458
[Lilia] <i>We've been cursed.</i>

19
00:01:00.542 --> 00:01:02.625
<i>The only way to end a curse is to face it.</i>

20
00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:04.708
I can kill it.

21
00:01:06.292 --> 00:01:07.917
<i>I feel lighter.</i>

22
00:01:08.417 --> 00:01:10.000
[Agatha] <i>What if we just call a truce?</i>

23
00:01:10.083 --> 00:01:12.792
Agatha? That boy isn't yours.

24
00:01:56.917 --> 00:02:00.667
[Salem Seven witches] Agatha Harkness.

25
00:02:03.083 --> 00:02:04.833
Find her.

26
00:02:05.875 --> 00:02:11.083
Agatha! Find her. Find them.

27
00:02:11.667 --> 00:02:16.500
Agatha Harkness. Agatha Harkness.

28
00:02:17.833 --> 00:02:19.542
[voices whispering indistinctly]

29
00:02:33.250 --> 00:02:34.500
[Lilia gasps]

30
00:02:35.958 --> 00:02:37.875
They're coming. We have to go.

31
00:02:38.750 --> 00:02:40.708
-What?
-The summoning spell.

32
00:02:40.792 --> 00:02:41.792
We left the door open.

33
00:02:42.375 --> 00:02:44.750
What are you talking about?
What did you see?

34
00:02:45.333 --> 00:02:48.042
Go on. Lilia. Tell them.

35
00:02:51.958 --> 00:02:53.917
-The Salem Seven.
-[Jen gasps]

36
00:02:54.500 --> 00:02:55.875
Scary black dresses?

37
00:02:57.625 --> 00:02:59.833
When Agatha killed her original coven...

38
00:02:59.917 --> 00:03:01.125
By stealing their power.

39
00:03:01.208 --> 00:03:03.792
Because her own mother tried
to have her executed.

40
00:03:03.875 --> 00:03:06.875
Are you really defending
a noted serial killer. you creepy lurker?

41
00:03:06.958 --> 00:03:08.833
Come on. someone finish the story.

42
00:03:08.917 --> 00:03:12.958
When Agatha murdered her sister witches.
she spared their young children.

43
00:03:13.042 --> 00:03:17.458
Yeah. and then they became a feral.
hive-minded coven bent on revenge.

44
00:03:17.667 --> 00:03:19.167
[Agatha] Whoa. ah!

45
00:03:19.250 --> 00:03:23.042
The moral of the story. kids.
is always finish what you started.

46
00:03:23.583 --> 00:03:25.667
Also. mercy is overrated.

47
00:03:25.750 --> 00:03:28.750
All right. everybody.
pack up your shit! Let's go!

48
00:03:30.958 --> 00:03:32.208
[wolf bays]

49
00:03:32.292 --> 00:03:33.875
-Oh. jeez!
-That was ahead of us.

50
00:03:34.417 --> 00:03:36.292
-[Salem Seven witch screeches]
-[Lilia screams]

51
00:03:36.375 --> 00:03:37.917
-That's behind us.
-We're trapped.

52
00:03:41.250 --> 00:03:42.250
What about a hexenbesen?

53
00:03:42.333 --> 00:03:43.667
-Horrible idea.
-Absolutely not.

54
00:03:43.750 --> 00:03:45.042
-[Rio] Yeah!
-That's a terrible idea.

55
00:03:45.125 --> 00:03:46.792
-Yes.
-Well. if you're all too cool

56
00:03:46.875 --> 00:03:48.500
for a practical means of escape...

57
00:03:48.667 --> 00:03:50.000
-[witches screech]
-[all gasp]

58
00:03:50.083 --> 00:03:52.458
-No. brooms are great.
-[Jen] No. no. no.

59
00:03:53.500 --> 00:03:55.875
This is so humiliating. Here.

60
00:03:57.083 --> 00:03:58.833
Why does your generation
hate them so much?

61
00:03:58.917 --> 00:04:02.417
[Lilia] Brooms have been co-opted
by the holiday industrial complex

62
00:04:02.500 --> 00:04:05.167
as an absurd emblem of our culture.

63
00:04:05.250 --> 00:04:09.250
Worse yet. they're an obvious symbol
of female domesticity.

64
00:04:09.333 --> 00:04:11.750
And they're basic.

65
00:04:12.458 --> 00:04:18.083
[chanting in Latin]

66
00:04:19.500 --> 00:04:22.625
-[in English] Oh. This is so cute.
-Thank you.

67
00:04:22.708 --> 00:04:23.833
You could have done better.

68
00:04:27.792 --> 00:04:29.292
It's about selflessness. Teen.

69
00:04:29.375 --> 00:04:31.000
Oh. is it? Tell us more.

70
00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:33.792
We fly together or not at all.

71
00:04:33.875 --> 00:04:34.875
[Alice] Hey.

72
00:04:37.958 --> 00:04:40.125
-I get one?
-If you give me one back. yeah.

73
00:04:40.208 --> 00:04:41.750
Yeah. Let me just... Oh!

74
00:04:46.417 --> 00:04:48.000
-All right. come on!
-There you go.

75
00:04:48.083 --> 00:04:49.125
[owl hoots]

76
00:04:52.667 --> 00:04:54.042
Oh. no.

77
00:04:55.417 --> 00:04:58.833
[all gasp and yell]

78
00:04:58.917 --> 00:05:00.667
Get off of him. [grunts]

79
00:05:02.208 --> 00:05:04.917
Teen. hurry! Just finish the ritual!
Finish the ritual!

80
00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:07.625
[both chanting in Latin]

81
00:05:07.708 --> 00:05:09.417
-[in English] We gotta go.
-All right. Let's go.

82
00:05:09.500 --> 00:05:11.833
-You okay?
-All right. Go. go! Okay.

83
00:05:12.125 --> 00:05:13.125
Whoo!

84
00:05:13.917 --> 00:05:15.667
-Wait. How do you do this?
-Keep up. Teen!

85
00:05:19.292 --> 00:05:20.375
[Teen] Okay. You got this.

86
00:05:20.875 --> 00:05:24.250
Oh. God! Oh. God! Oh. God!

87
00:05:24.333 --> 00:05:27.083
Try praying to the Divine Mother. kiddo!

88
00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:33.792
[screeches]

89
00:05:35.167 --> 00:05:36.667
We got to get off The Road.

90
00:05:37.167 --> 00:05:38.625
Move!

91
00:05:48.792 --> 00:05:50.292
[exclaims]

92
00:05:51.042 --> 00:05:53.458
[Lilia] This is incredible.

93
00:05:54.792 --> 00:05:56.583
[Lilia laughs]

94
00:05:59.833 --> 00:06:01.833
I haven't done this in centuries.

95
00:06:15.458 --> 00:06:17.208
Why haven't we been doing this all along?

96
00:06:22.208 --> 00:06:24.625
[all exclaim]

97
00:06:24.708 --> 00:06:26.292
What's going on?

98
00:06:26.375 --> 00:06:29.625
It's The Road. It's forcing us down.

99
00:06:29.708 --> 00:06:31.750
-[Alice] We're going to crash...
-[Rio] My God!

100
00:06:32.375 --> 00:06:33.625
[Jen] It won't let us leave!

101
00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:35.875
[screaming]

102
00:06:35.958 --> 00:06:37.333
[laughing]

103
00:06:38.167 --> 00:06:39.708
[Alice] Oh. my God!

104
00:06:41.667 --> 00:06:43.583
[Agatha] Okay. We're okay.

105
00:06:46.208 --> 00:06:47.292
The next trial!

106
00:06:54.583 --> 00:06:56.708
-[screeches]
-[all screaming]

107
00:06:56.792 --> 00:06:57.875
[Teen] Oh. my God!

108
00:07:01.958 --> 00:07:03.000
[Jen] Hurry!

109
00:07:03.083 --> 00:07:06.000
[Agatha] Hurry. go. go. go!

110
00:07:07.833 --> 00:07:09.333
[all gasping]

111
00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:14.833
[Agatha groans] Oh. my God!

112
00:07:15.958 --> 00:07:18.625
Okay. All right. Okay. Okay.

113
00:07:25.667 --> 00:07:27.042
We're okay.

114
00:07:27.208 --> 00:07:30.583
No. we're not! The entire
Halloween aisle's outside waiting for us.

115
00:07:30.667 --> 00:07:33.708
And it doesn't look like
they can get in. does it?

116
00:07:35.042 --> 00:07:38.292
So all we have to do is complete the trial

117
00:07:38.375 --> 00:07:41.792
and continue on
before they can reach us. Okay?

118
00:07:42.792 --> 00:07:45.250
How? Kiss. Marry. Kill?

119
00:07:47.167 --> 00:07:50.333
-My spell book. I can't find it.
-Where'd you have it the last time?

120
00:07:51.833 --> 00:07:52.958
Flying on a broom.

121
00:07:53.042 --> 00:07:55.042
Forget it. You can take
the training wheels off.

122
00:08:07.833 --> 00:08:09.042
Whose trial is this?

123
00:08:09.875 --> 00:08:12.375
[chuckles] Agatha's.

124
00:08:15.417 --> 00:08:16.458
[Teen] How do you know?

125
00:08:16.542 --> 00:08:18.000
A blood moon.

126
00:08:18.833 --> 00:08:22.667
When the veil between the living
and the dead is at its thinnest.

127
00:08:24.125 --> 00:08:26.542
[Teen] Wait. I thought talking to the dead
was your department.

128
00:08:26.667 --> 00:08:30.333
Oh. common misconception.
I read people. I read time.

129
00:08:30.417 --> 00:08:32.583
But talking to spirits was just a con.

130
00:08:33.333 --> 00:08:35.208
And who better to commune with the dead

131
00:08:35.292 --> 00:08:37.667
than someone who's put so many
in the grave?

132
00:08:48.583 --> 00:08:49.583
We have to Ouija.

133
00:08:50.167 --> 00:08:51.458
-[watch alarm beeps]
-[gasps]

134
00:08:55.417 --> 00:08:56.792
It's not a verb.

135
00:08:56.875 --> 00:08:58.417
[Teen] Come on. We have to do this.

136
00:09:04.958 --> 00:09:07.375
Uh. Spanish. Chinese...

137
00:09:07.500 --> 00:09:09.500
Ah. English.

138
00:09:11.125 --> 00:09:14.917
Okay. "Number one.
do not use the Ouija board alone.

139
00:09:15.708 --> 00:09:18.208
"Number two.
do not speak over each other."

140
00:09:18.292 --> 00:09:20.000
It's not written there. Show me that.

141
00:09:20.083 --> 00:09:23.250
"Three! Do not taunt the spirits."

142
00:09:25.458 --> 00:09:26.458
What?

143
00:09:26.958 --> 00:09:30.458
I repeat. do not taunt the spirits.

144
00:09:31.167 --> 00:09:33.208
"Four. do not ask about death.

145
00:09:33.292 --> 00:09:36.417
"Five. always end your session
with goodbye.

146
00:09:36.500 --> 00:09:40.958
"Six. do not. under any circumstances.
remove your hand from the planchette.

147
00:09:42.333 --> 00:09:44.333
"If you do so. a spirit will be released."

148
00:09:49.250 --> 00:09:50.500
What does it say on the back?

149
00:09:51.750 --> 00:09:52.833
"For ages three and up."

150
00:09:54.583 --> 00:09:55.667
Okay.

151
00:09:59.708 --> 00:10:01.000
Wonder who's waiting for you.

152
00:10:02.792 --> 00:10:04.292
And with what trauma.

153
00:10:05.792 --> 00:10:10.667
Pff! It could be literally anybody. So...

154
00:10:15.875 --> 00:10:17.250
[clears throat]

155
00:10:28.458 --> 00:10:30.500
Mother. Maiden. Crone.

156
00:10:32.208 --> 00:10:34.208
spirits be known.

157
00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:39.375
I can hear something. Shh!

158
00:10:43.417 --> 00:10:45.583
Oh. my God. I'm not moving it.
Are you moving it?

159
00:10:45.667 --> 00:10:46.875
[shushing]

160
00:10:47.667 --> 00:10:49.667
Is someone here with us

161
00:10:51.042 --> 00:10:53.375
during this Witching Hour?

162
00:10:58.875 --> 00:11:00.125
[Jen] Yes.

163
00:11:01.667 --> 00:11:02.667
All right.

164
00:11:02.750 --> 00:11:03.958
And who.

165
00:11:05.125 --> 00:11:06.167
may I ask.

166
00:11:06.917 --> 00:11:10.083
do we have the pleasure of communing with?

167
00:11:13.917 --> 00:11:16.333
[Teen] M. R.

168
00:11:17.500 --> 00:11:19.625
S. H.

169
00:11:21.583 --> 00:11:22.583
A.

170
00:11:23.167 --> 00:11:25.500
R. T.

171
00:11:25.833 --> 00:11:27.583
[Jen gasps] Mrs. Hart?

172
00:11:30.417 --> 00:11:32.958
Hey. girl. feeling better?

173
00:11:33.667 --> 00:11:35.375
How's your face?

174
00:11:35.458 --> 00:11:36.667
No taunting.

175
00:11:37.083 --> 00:11:38.625
[all gasp]

176
00:11:38.708 --> 00:11:41.292
-Your hands. What did you do?
-I didn't do it!

177
00:11:42.542 --> 00:11:44.542
-Agatha?
-[gasps]

178
00:11:45.458 --> 00:11:46.958
[warbling]

179
00:11:52.417 --> 00:11:53.875
[in Mrs. Hart's voice] Oh. my.

180
00:11:55.625 --> 00:11:57.542
What a journey.

181
00:11:59.500 --> 00:12:04.792
[sighs] There I was.
living my tiny life in the burbs.

182
00:12:05.708 --> 00:12:07.542
baking casseroles.

183
00:12:08.375 --> 00:12:13.042
linking in to conspiracy theories
on Facebook.

184
00:12:13.125 --> 00:12:15.167
drinking before noon.

185
00:12:15.250 --> 00:12:17.292
and there you were

186
00:12:18.042 --> 00:12:20.875
bringing chills and thrills

187
00:12:21.917 --> 00:12:25.792
and bringing on my own early demise!

188
00:12:27.333 --> 00:12:28.917
Listen. Mrs. Hart...

189
00:12:29.000 --> 00:12:31.292
-She's not Mrs. Hart.
-She's Sharon Davis.

190
00:12:31.375 --> 00:12:33.875
I am. I'm Sharon Davis.

191
00:12:33.958 --> 00:12:35.000
-She's Agatha.
-Yeah.

192
00:12:35.083 --> 00:12:36.375
What? [giggles]

193
00:12:37.000 --> 00:12:38.000
She's just scared.

194
00:12:42.875 --> 00:12:44.125
[clears throat]

195
00:12:44.625 --> 00:12:45.625
[in normal voice] Okay.

196
00:12:46.708 --> 00:12:48.958
-I thought that was pretty good.
-The clock is ticking.

197
00:12:49.500 --> 00:12:50.500
[tapping floor]

198
00:12:52.583 --> 00:12:54.042
Fine.

199
00:12:56.167 --> 00:12:58.042
Well. let's get to it. Right?

200
00:13:02.292 --> 00:13:04.083
Maiden. Mother. Crone.

201
00:13:07.042 --> 00:13:08.833
spirits be known.

202
00:13:11.792 --> 00:13:13.750
-[ceiling rustling]
-[all gasping softly]

203
00:13:18.500 --> 00:13:20.208
Who is here with us tonight?

204
00:13:20.583 --> 00:13:21.958
[whooshing]

205
00:13:22.333 --> 00:13:24.500
D. E.

206
00:13:25.083 --> 00:13:27.583
-A. T...
-A. T...

207
00:13:28.667 --> 00:13:30.042
H. Death.

208
00:13:31.208 --> 00:13:32.458
[laughs]

209
00:13:32.667 --> 00:13:35.042
-We're not supposed to ask about death.
-[all shush]

210
00:13:37.708 --> 00:13:38.958
What do you want?

211
00:13:40.208 --> 00:13:46.875
P. U. N. I. S. H.

212
00:13:48.333 --> 00:13:49.333
Punish.

213
00:13:54.542 --> 00:13:55.792
Who do you wanna punish?

214
00:13:57.083 --> 00:14:00.125
[all] A. G. A...

215
00:14:00.208 --> 00:14:03.375
-T. H...
-Stop. All right. stop.

216
00:14:04.458 --> 00:14:08.333
A. G. A. T. H. A.

217
00:14:08.417 --> 00:14:09.958
-Stop. Make it stop!
-A. G. A.

218
00:14:10.042 --> 00:14:12.792
-T. H...
-Stop making it do that!

219
00:14:12.875 --> 00:14:17.250
-Stop it! Stop it! Stop it!
-[others arguing]

220
00:14:17.333 --> 00:14:18.458
I can't!

221
00:14:18.542 --> 00:14:19.917
What are you doing?

222
00:14:20.708 --> 00:14:22.167
[all scream]

223
00:14:28.583 --> 00:14:30.000
-[voices shrieking]
-Make it stop!

224
00:14:30.083 --> 00:14:31.583
I would if I could!

225
00:14:31.667 --> 00:14:34.000
I hated this the first time!

226
00:14:34.083 --> 00:14:35.750
Lilia's being weird again.

227
00:14:35.833 --> 00:14:36.833
What do they want?

228
00:14:37.333 --> 00:14:38.833
They already told us.

229
00:14:41.833 --> 00:14:43.458
Punish Agatha!

230
00:14:49.875 --> 00:14:53.208
Meaning. we need to...

231
00:14:55.292 --> 00:14:56.292
Yup.

232
00:14:57.625 --> 00:14:59.000
It's how we pass the trial.

233
00:14:59.875 --> 00:15:01.625
Uh. I don't think so.

234
00:15:01.708 --> 00:15:03.125
And after everything she's done.

235
00:15:04.042 --> 00:15:10.000
the lies. the cheating.
the complete and utter lack of humanity.

236
00:15:10.083 --> 00:15:13.250
-No. there has to be another way.
-Right. Yes.

237
00:15:13.333 --> 00:15:15.375
-We could tie her up.
-You're not serious.

238
00:15:15.458 --> 00:15:17.417
-I can't...
-Humiliation would work too.

239
00:15:17.917 --> 00:15:19.667
I mean. or we could just slit her throat.

240
00:15:21.042 --> 00:15:23.375
When people ask me
why I don't have female friends...

241
00:15:24.417 --> 00:15:27.792
But we were getting along. weren't we?
We were clicking. There was unity.

242
00:15:27.875 --> 00:15:29.500
Familiars don't get a vote.

243
00:15:34.333 --> 00:15:35.375
[Lilia] What?

244
00:15:35.875 --> 00:15:37.333
Where'd she go?

245
00:15:37.417 --> 00:15:38.542
[all gasp]

246
00:15:38.625 --> 00:15:40.000
Oh. my gosh. what's happening?

247
00:15:41.042 --> 00:15:44.583
Agatha. Let's talk about this
for a minute.

248
00:15:45.375 --> 00:15:47.292
We're sisters in the craft. remember?

249
00:15:49.000 --> 00:15:50.000
[Alice] We need light.

250
00:16:03.125 --> 00:16:05.500
-[voice breathing heavily]
-Does anyone else hear that?

251
00:16:17.792 --> 00:16:19.458
[all screaming]

252
00:16:26.333 --> 00:16:27.500
She's faking it.

253
00:16:27.583 --> 00:16:29.083
[Alice] Look at her face!

254
00:16:29.625 --> 00:16:31.667
Sweetheart. you okay?

255
00:16:32.667 --> 00:16:33.875
[Teen] Oh. my gosh.

256
00:16:33.958 --> 00:16:35.542
[Alice] Not faking! Not faking!

257
00:16:35.625 --> 00:16:37.250
[Rio] What's she doin'? Where's she goin'?

258
00:16:37.333 --> 00:16:39.375
[Teen] That is not Agatha!

259
00:16:39.917 --> 00:16:43.042
-She's possessed! For real this time!
-[barks]

260
00:16:43.125 --> 00:16:44.167
[Jen] Hey. over here!

261
00:16:46.042 --> 00:16:47.500
-[gasps]
-[Teen] No!

262
00:16:51.167 --> 00:16:52.667
[Alice] Stop it! Let her go!

263
00:16:54.083 --> 00:16:55.875
-What are you doing? You're hurting her.
-[choking]

264
00:17:00.250 --> 00:17:03.583
-[Alice] Jen. Jen. Okay. okay. Where...
-[Rio] Agatha!

265
00:17:05.958 --> 00:17:08.042
Where is she? All right. Where is she?

266
00:17:08.792 --> 00:17:10.542
Agatha!

267
00:17:12.958 --> 00:17:14.458
[all gasping]

268
00:17:19.292 --> 00:17:20.292
What is that?

269
00:17:25.833 --> 00:17:27.958
That is a ghost.

270
00:17:29.958 --> 00:17:31.458
I hate ghosts.

271
00:17:31.542 --> 00:17:32.958
Who... Who are you?

272
00:17:33.958 --> 00:17:37.542
<i>Evanora Harkness of the Salemites.</i>

273
00:17:39.542 --> 00:17:41.250
[Agatha] Hey. Mom.

274
00:17:45.958 --> 00:17:50.042
It was nice having you in my body
for a second there.

275
00:17:50.792 --> 00:17:54.125
I've never felt so close to you before.

276
00:17:55.833 --> 00:17:58.875
<i>My coven risked everything to kill her.</i>

277
00:17:59.375 --> 00:18:02.458
<i>And you fools have willingly joined her.</i>

278
00:18:03.208 --> 00:18:06.375
Stop embarrassing me
in front of my friends. Mom.

279
00:18:06.958 --> 00:18:09.417
So what do we do? Do we banish her?

280
00:18:09.500 --> 00:18:11.458
[Lilia] Emotion ties them to this plane.

281
00:18:12.042 --> 00:18:14.208
They have unfinished business.

282
00:18:14.292 --> 00:18:15.750
So let's finish her business.

283
00:18:15.833 --> 00:18:17.917
-[Jen] Okay.
-[Teen] What do you want?

284
00:18:18.000 --> 00:18:21.542
<i>You must finish the Witches' Road</i>

285
00:18:22.208 --> 00:18:23.875
<i>without Agatha.</i>

286
00:18:25.167 --> 00:18:28.625
She means punish Agatha.

287
00:18:29.375 --> 00:18:31.417
<i>Leave her with me.</i>

288
00:18:32.083 --> 00:18:34.250
No. No way.

289
00:18:34.333 --> 00:18:36.542
A minute ago you were ready
to slit her throat.

290
00:18:36.625 --> 00:18:38.250
Yeah. well. her mother can't have her.

291
00:18:46.667 --> 00:18:47.833
Mom?

292
00:19:00.708 --> 00:19:02.375
Why do you hate me still?

293
00:19:04.083 --> 00:19:05.583
<i>You were born evil.</i>

294
00:19:08.417 --> 00:19:10.833
<i>I ought to have killed you
the moment you left my body.</i>

295
00:19:21.375 --> 00:19:22.542
We have to go.

296
00:19:23.292 --> 00:19:25.375
-Jen.
-No. no.

297
00:19:26.167 --> 00:19:28.042
There's no flood here. There's no fire.

298
00:19:28.625 --> 00:19:33.125
The only danger to us in this trial
is Agatha Harkness.

299
00:19:33.958 --> 00:19:34.958
Please take me with you.

300
00:19:35.583 --> 00:19:39.583
-Don't. Let me. Please. Don't go!
-We can't leave her here. No. no.

301
00:19:39.667 --> 00:19:41.250
Take me with you. Please.

302
00:19:41.333 --> 00:19:44.667
Don't leave me with her.
I can be good. Please!

303
00:19:47.250 --> 00:19:48.250
No. not again!

304
00:19:49.667 --> 00:19:52.125
Leave her alone. [grunts]

305
00:19:54.292 --> 00:19:55.458
-Knight of Wands.
-No!

306
00:19:58.292 --> 00:19:59.792
[groans]

307
00:20:04.375 --> 00:20:06.917
-No!
-[Alice groaning]

308
00:20:08.917 --> 00:20:10.917
[Lilia yells] No!

309
00:20:13.000 --> 00:20:14.000
Alice!

310
00:20:15.000 --> 00:20:16.708
Just stop! Make her stop!

311
00:20:24.333 --> 00:20:25.333
Who are you?

312
00:20:25.417 --> 00:20:27.958
N. I. C.

313
00:20:28.042 --> 00:20:32.125
H. O. L. A. S. S. C. R. A. T.

314
00:20:32.208 --> 00:20:33.750
C. H.

315
00:20:34.833 --> 00:20:36.958
-Nicholas Scratch.
-[watch beeps]

316
00:20:38.375 --> 00:20:39.500
Nicholas Scratch!

317
00:20:42.417 --> 00:20:45.292
[Nicholas] <i>Mama! Stop.</i>

318
00:20:55.750 --> 00:20:57.542
[watch alarm beeping]

319
00:21:07.875 --> 00:21:11.458
Alice. Alice. Wake up.
Alice. please wake up. Alice!

320
00:21:12.667 --> 00:21:16.792
Alice. come on.
Alice. come on. Wake up. Alice.

321
00:21:16.875 --> 00:21:20.083
Alice. please. Please wake up.
Alice. Wake...

322
00:21:20.167 --> 00:21:21.500
Don't touch her!

323
00:21:22.208 --> 00:21:23.458
She was protecting you.

324
00:21:24.750 --> 00:21:25.792
But you don't deserve it.

325
00:21:29.417 --> 00:21:30.417
I didn't.

326
00:21:32.125 --> 00:21:36.958
[Teen] Come on. Wake up.
Wake up. Alice. Alice.

327
00:21:37.042 --> 00:21:38.750
What can you do?

328
00:21:38.833 --> 00:21:41.000
-Nothing.
-[Teen] What about your panacea?

329
00:21:41.083 --> 00:21:42.458
-It's too late.
-No. it's not!

330
00:21:42.542 --> 00:21:45.042
There's a spell. there's always a spell!

331
00:21:45.125 --> 00:21:48.375
Alice. please wake up.
Alice! Alice! Come on. Alice. Come on.

332
00:21:50.583 --> 00:21:51.625
She's gone.

333
00:22:34.042 --> 00:22:37.250
-Hey! How could you?
-I...

334
00:22:37.333 --> 00:22:41.333
-How could you kill her?
-I couldn't... I couldn't control it.

335
00:22:41.417 --> 00:22:43.750
Yes. you could have. Don't lie to me.

336
00:22:45.250 --> 00:22:46.250
I'm not.

337
00:22:46.333 --> 00:22:47.500
You wanted her power.

338
00:22:48.750 --> 00:22:51.125
That's what this has always been about
for you. isn't it?

339
00:22:52.333 --> 00:22:53.333
[Jen] Of course it is.

340
00:22:54.042 --> 00:22:55.333
That's what all this is about.

341
00:22:57.333 --> 00:22:58.458
For any of us.

342
00:23:01.875 --> 00:23:05.042
Death comes for us all.

343
00:23:08.417 --> 00:23:09.917
That's what it means to be a witch?

344
00:23:11.125 --> 00:23:13.250
Killing people to serve your own agenda?

345
00:23:14.292 --> 00:23:17.083
No. Not for me.

346
00:23:23.292 --> 00:23:24.292
[snickers]

347
00:23:37.375 --> 00:23:39.083
[whispers] Are you sure?

348
00:23:53.458 --> 00:23:56.042
You're so much like your mother.

349
00:24:13.167 --> 00:24:15.667
Come. Pet.

350
00:24:23.583 --> 00:24:25.750
Wait. what are you... Stop!

351
00:24:25.833 --> 00:24:28.458
Wait! Stop! Why are you... What?

352
00:24:28.542 --> 00:24:30.333
Why? What is... Teen. stop!

353
00:24:31.250 --> 00:24:33.625
Stop! Somebody! Let go of me!

354
00:24:34.208 --> 00:24:35.208
[screams]

355
00:24:38.125 --> 00:24:39.833
Wait! Help me!

356
00:24:43.042 --> 00:24:45.417
[screams] Help me! Help me!

357
00:24:52.542 --> 00:24:54.542
-No!
-[both scream]

358
00:24:57.167 --> 00:24:58.625
[Lilia] No! What's happening?

359
00:24:58.708 --> 00:25:01.917
-[Jen screams]
-[Lilia] No. no. no. No. no!

360
00:25:13.167 --> 00:25:15.458
[♪ "You Should See Me in a Crown"
by Billie Eilish playing]

